{"tid":1676523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下個星期只可以有 一至兩個小活動 其他全力搞1102","createTime":"2019-10-26T13:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T07:33:09.000Z","uid":94771,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cd44c733531e27a16760310f168cc4953e2169b6","tid":1676523,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"來緊重點應該係<br />\n1031<br />\n毋忘831恐襲 / 還我831真相<br />\n<br />\n1102 <br />\n流水式維園集會<br />\n<br />\n唔好再放文宣力量係其他小活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02eb4e4f7eb9bf5a85b27fabafece6226905e141","tid":1676523,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"10d2fa6f44f95921ffd7042dd56c01ad3f1815e9","tid":1676523,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"我真係唔想製造一個廢post, 所以我唔會開post 評論某間米線店<br />\n我直接係唔同post 屌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我唔撚知你係五毛、風向撚定係戇鳩，但係開post 之前可唔可以用個死人腦諗下野</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係2019年10月26日，標題有「譚仔」嘅post，有超過100個，我數到100個就停撚左，因為我覺得真係好撚on9</span></span><br />\n推今晚集會post 又唔見你咁勤力？<br />\n推聽日尖沙咀集會又唔見你會咁勤力？<br />\n一間咁嘅濕鳩食肆，一間咁大間嘅食肆唔通奶共會唔知咩<br />\n洗唔洗幾百個post 一齊討論呀屌<br />\n<br />\n爭氣d 啦，唔好犀比班濕鳩五毛睇<br />\n多啲獨立思考，拒絕風向<br />\n光復香港唔係靠熱血就夠，仲要智慧架大佬<br />\n一齊努力，要班五毛無糧出"},{"pid":"b6b405226747b03f4681dd0f8dde4368091fb1ed","tid":1676523,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehhREJj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FehhREJj.jpg&h=75b8dbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T53tGWF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT53tGW